  "texts": [
    "In Section 4.4, we discuss design choices of the reward signal that make RL most robust and effective.",
    "We fine-tuned a Llama 4 Maverick model to generate rubrics for prompts.",
    "For training, we collected thousands of human-expert annotated rubrics for a separate set of user prompts via Surge.",
    "We formatted these user prompts and their corresponding rubrics into SFT data and trained the Llama 4 Maverick model for one epoch.",
    "For evaluation, we used a hold-out set of human annotations."
  ],
